<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 06:20:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>巴西中场奥斯卡重返圣保罗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/brazilian-midfielder-oscar-returns-sao-paulo-2024-12-25/</link><description>巴西意甲球队周二表示，前切尔西中场球员奥斯卡将以三年合同回到他的前俱乐部圣保罗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 04:38:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/brazilian-midfielder-oscar-returns-sao-paulo-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>尽管销量增长，丰田全球产量连续第十个月下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-global-production-down-10th-month-despite-rising-sales-2024-12-25/</link><description>日本汽车制造商丰田汽车周三表示，尽管由于美国和中国需求强劲，其全球销量连续第二个月增长，但该公司 11 月份全球产量连续第 10 个月下降。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 04:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-global-production-down-10th-month-despite-rising-sales-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中方谴责菲律宾防长就中美导弹问题发表言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-philippine-defence-chiefs-remarks-china-us-missiles-2024-12-25/</link><description>中国周三谴责菲律宾国防部长有关中国的言论，称其为“毫无根据的指控”，“恶意攻击”中国执政的共产党。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 03:57:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-condemns-philippine-defence-chiefs-remarks-china-us-missiles-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>中日外长北京会晤 海鲜贸易提上议程</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-seafood-trade-agenda-2024-12-25/</link><description>随着日本外务大臣访问中国，预计海鲜贸易将被提上议程。中国是日本最大的水产品出口市场，直到北京禁止水产品出口以抗议东京向海洋排放处理过的放射性废水。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 01:03:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-seafood-trade-agenda-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大谴责中国就维吾尔族和西藏问题针对加拿大机构采取的措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-condemns-chinas-steps-against-canadian-institutions-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-24/</link><description>加拿大政府周二谴责中国对涉及维吾尔族和西藏人权问题的两家加拿大机构和20名人士采取措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 21:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-condemns-chinas-steps-against-canadian-institutions-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国药明康德将在美国限制下出售先进疗法部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-sell-advanced-therapies-unit-us-private-equity-firm-2024-12-24/</link><description>中国药明康德周二表示，其子公司已与美国私募股权公司 Altaris LLC 签署协议，出售其细胞和基因治疗制造部门 WuXi Advanced Therapies，交易金额未公开。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 14:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-sell-advanced-therapies-unit-us-private-equity-firm-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>本田和日产的合作需要双方都抽不出时间的东西：时间</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/honda-nissan-tie-up-requires-something-neither-can-spare-time-2024-12-24/</link><description>本田和日产希望通过合并创建世界第三大汽车集团而获得巨大收益，但来自中国的激烈竞争引发了人们对合并能否及时实现的疑问。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 13:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/honda-nissan-tie-up-requires-something-neither-can-spare-time-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>随着主要国家吝惜援助，全球饥饿危机加深</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/global-hunger-crisis-deepens-major-nations-skimp-aid-2024-12-24/</link><description>这是一个简单但残酷的等式：世界各地挨饿或陷入困境的人数正在增加，而世界上最富有的国家为帮助他们而提供的资金却在下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 11:12:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/global-hunger-crisis-deepens-major-nations-skimp-aid-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国和日本预计周三讨论海鲜禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-expected-discuss-seafood-ban-wednesday-2024-12-24/</link><description>中国外交部表示，中国外交部长王毅将于周三在北京与日本外长岩屋毅举行会谈，预计两人将讨论中国对日本海鲜进口的禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 08:50:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-expected-discuss-seafood-ban-wednesday-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾捍卫美国部署的导弹系统，寻求拥有自己的导弹系统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-defends-us-missile-system-deployment-seeks-acquire-its-own-2024-12-24/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周二证明该国部署美国中程导弹系统的合理性，并计划购买自己的中程导弹系统，尽管遭到南海长期竞争对手中国的反对。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 07:42:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-defends-us-missile-system-deployment-seeks-acquire-its-own-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>曼联杯主席表示，尽管退役，但比赛仍处于良好状态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/game-good-hands-despite-high-profile-retirements-says-united-cup-chief-2024-12-24/</link><description>这项价值 1000 万美元的混合团体赛事颇受欢迎，旨在在周五新赛季拉开帷幕时培养新人才。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 07:31:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/game-good-hands-despite-high-profile-retirements-says-united-cup-chief-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国宁德时代推出电动底盘，将安全性作为首要卖点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-catl-launches-ev-platform-flagging-safety-top-selling-point-2024-12-24/</link><description>全球最大的电动汽车电池制造商中国宁德时代 (CATL) 周二推出了一款新的电动汽车底盘，据称该底盘可承受 120 公里/小时（75 英里/小时）的正面碰撞，而不会着火或爆炸，并将安全性作为关键卖点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 06:28:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-catl-launches-ev-platform-flagging-safety-top-selling-point-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国计划明年发行创纪录的4110亿美元特别国债</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-411-bln-special-treasury-bond-issuance-next-year-sources-say-2024-12-24/</link><description>此举出台之际，北京正准备缓解唐纳德·特朗普一月份重返白宫时美国对中国进口商品加征关税的预期所带来的打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 05:41:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-plans-411-bln-special-treasury-bond-issuance-next-year-sources-say-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>香港在安全压力下悬赏另外六名民主党人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-offers-bounties-six-more-democrats-security-squeeze-2024-12-24/</link><description>香港周二向另外六名被认为违反国家安全法的民主运动人士悬赏 100 万港元（合 128,728 美元），并吊销了另外七人的护照，同时这个亚洲金融中心仍在继续开展安全行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 05:16:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-offers-bounties-six-more-democrats-security-squeeze-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国明年将加大消费财政支持力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-increase-budget-deficit-ramp-up-govt-bond-issuance-support-growth-2024-12-24/</link><description>财政部表示，中国还将加大对消费品以旧换新的支持力度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 04:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-increase-budget-deficit-ramp-up-govt-bond-issuance-support-growth-2024-12-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>